    <h2 class="h2" id="sec-2-h" style="margin-bottom:18px;">2. Independence from Intuit</h2>
    <div class="prose">
      <p><strong>TechBrot Inc. is an independent Certified QuickBooks ProAdvisor firm. TechBrot Inc. is not owned, operated, employed, endorsed, sponsored by, or otherwise affiliated with Intuit Inc.</strong></p>
      <p>TechBrot&rsquo;s personnel hold active Intuit QuickBooks ProAdvisor certifications, which are professional credentials issued by Intuit and verifiable through Intuit&rsquo;s public ProAdvisor directory. Holding such certifications does not make TechBrot an agent, representative, reseller, or affiliate of Intuit. Any engagement you enter into with TechBrot is solely with TechBrot Inc. (or, where applicable, with an independent operator in TechBrot&rsquo;s network), and not with Intuit Inc.</p>
      <p>Because TechBrot is independent, its recommendations regarding software platforms, plans, and configurations are made in the interest of the client&rsquo;s business needs and are not directed by any vendor relationship.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="sec reveal" id="sec-3" style="padding-top:24px;" aria-labelledby="sec-3-h">
