      <p>Statements regarding response times, turnaround, or service standards (for example, discovery-call scheduling, written-scope delivery timeframes, or diagnostic availability) describe TechBrot&rsquo;s operating intentions and are not contractual guarantees unless expressly stated as such in a signed engagement agreement.</p>
